{"tid":592933,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"北角貨櫃寫字樓爆炸 女子燒傷送院亡","createTime":"2018-03-14T15:15:41.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-14T15:50:48.000Z","uid":41052,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"4b657f54e1968caca1113130f35a417e9dad92e7","tid":592933,"uid":41052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-14T15:15:41.000Z","msg":"北角發生火警，晚上8時許，北角碼頭旁地盤一個貨櫃寫字樓起火，其間傳出爆炸聲。消防接報到場開喉射水灌救，並在火場內救出一名女子，她嚴重燒傷，由救護車送往律敦治醫院搶救，惟抵院後證實不治。消防正調查起火原因。<br />\n<br />\n據悉，死者年約50歲，在地盤內任職女工。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180314/57947191\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180314%2F57947191&d=tGUmkzaQjrZs4McMo98rlgdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=245bb72d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180314%2F57947191&h=c31846d2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180314/57947191</a>"},{"pid":"70e0ef756022bd9091f4190173a77d88b0b780d0","tid":592933,"uid":53026,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-14T15:50:48.000Z","msg":"地盤都要OT?"}]}